price can suffer severe multiple compression."}}]}, {"@type": "Article", "headline": "Top Growth Stocks 2025 Outlook", "description": "Growth investing is changing. These 15 hyper-growth stocks have the precise catalysts needed to dominate 2025. See the controversial #1 pick.", "author": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "Westmount Fundamentals"}}]};
